Version 0.4

- configuration as CMake project
- icon size configurable in config file
- buttons hidable by commenting out entry in config file
- default shutdown commands changed from sudo to dbus calls
- manpage added

Version 0.3

- initial release as extended fork of exitx
- icons changed from .h style to configurable external icons
- icons recreated basing on Faenza grey theme
- config file in /etc for configuration of commands and icons